1. start a server, make sure to allow both http,https and start nginx (systemctl start nginx)
2. install nginx, certbot, python-certbot-nginx
3. start nginx
4. send my your public IP
3. certbot certonly --nginx
4. see /etc/letsencrypt/renewal/<yourname>.omarwsaleh.com.conf
   a. to see where is the private key and the certificate
5. edit /etc/nginx/nginx.conf  to uncommend the ssl section and add necessary details
6. nginx -t > to verify the configuratin 
7. systemctl reload nginx




